description:
Cold Case



Aired on 04/12/2010, Narrated by Jonathan Aris



On 10 March 1989, Air Ontario Flight 1363, a Fokker F28-1000, crashes just after take off, killing 24 people.
Three years later,
On 22 March 1992, USAir Flight 405, another Fokker F28-1000, also crashes just after take off in similar conditions to Flight 1363.
